<br>
If a mob is resisting me badly, I'll try to stun, tash, mez. Usually the mez after tash sticks.<br>
<br>
As far as mez duration, I have to disagree. I used to use a stopwatch to time my mezzes in order to get a good sense on their duration. Not a single mez has ever "broken" early unless it was damaged. I still use the stopwatch when I use an AE mez on a big crowd, since 6 mezzes breaking at once = death unless lucky ). Fascination lasts 36 secs on the dot, every time, no matter what my cha is.<br>
<br>
Just my observations. <p><img src="http://miragia.homestead.com/files/miragia.gif">
