<br>
1) Level of the mob compared to the caster<br>
2) Magic resistance level of the mob <br>
3) Charisma<br>
<br>
In my experience assuming a normal level of MR in the mob a chanter gets good mezzing at 170+ on blue mobs. If you are having to mezz yellows and low red you will need 200+ Cha.<br>
<br>
The wrinkle in this is that not all mobs are as resistant as others and so some mobs you can mezz low reds with ease...but some blue mobs prove to be very difficult.<br>
<br>
Leir <br>
60th Lvl Enchanter <br>
<br>
