<br>
Being 55 and seeing I have C2, ToT, and Wandering Mind.. usually with all the caster mobs in Seb I am rarely LoM even with buffing and mezzing. Granted there may be places with no caster types to tap from... C2 has a decent enough mana regen time for me to do my job with int around 173-182.. so mana isn't a problem if you can manage it wisely.<br>
<br>
Now as for charisma.. I notice this: Less resists when I am at 182 than when Im nakie  with like 110 charisma (I didn't know a lick about chanters when creating mine and at 55 am not going to start over). As for mezzing/charms based on charisma.. mezzes don't last longer or shorter they just stick more with higher charisma.. charms do not last longer or shorter *However*.. it is like invis.. charm is random.. but with higher charisma you have a better chance at it lasting its full duration.  That's my 2 cp worth.. I did practice in seb a bit with like 20 spawns of krup shaman.. 10 nakie 10 fully buffed.. out of the 10 I was nakie.. a lot more resists than when I was buffed up on charisma.  Happy hunting to you all. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ubowynn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bowynn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#330000>(8/16/01 10:57:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=55.topic&index=40>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.visveres.com/ezboard/members/bowynn1.jpg width=118 hieght=191></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RE:</span><hr size=1> My opinion:<br>
